# AirGuard TN — Data Authenticity Report

> What is real, what is scaled, what is mocked, what is fake.

---

## Authenticity Legend

| Level | Tag | Meaning |
|-------|-----|---------|
| 🟢 | **LIVE** | Real data fetched from a public API at runtime, no modification |
| 🔵 | **REAL + SCALED** | Real API data with a multiplicative correction factor applied |
| 🟡 | **REAL + SYNTHETIC JITTER** | Real base value with random noise added for spatial variation |
| 🟠 | **HARDCODED FALLBACK** | Handwritten coordinates/values, not from any data source |
| 🔴 | **FULLY SYNTHETIC** | Invented numbers, no API involved |

---

