## 4. Danger Score

| Item | Source | Tag | Detail |
|------|--------|-----|--------|
| NO₂ component | 🟡 From model prediction + jitter | **SYNTHETIC JITTER** | Based on jittered per-cell NO₂ |
| Wind component | 🟢 From live API | **LIVE** | Real wind speed |
| BLH component | 🟢 From live API | **LIVE** | Real boundary layer height |
| Inversion flag | 🟢 Computed from real BLH/temp | **LIVE** | `BLH < 500m` or `T_850 > T_surface` |
| **Score formula weights** | 🔴 Manually tuned | **SYNTHETIC** | Weights (0.45, 0.30, 0.15) were hand-chosen. Not derived from any data. |

