## 5. Weather Flags

| Flag | Source | Tag | Detail |
|------|--------|-----|--------|
| `inversion_flag` | 🟢 Computed from real BLH + T_850hPa | **LIVE** | Fires on 84% of days (normal coastal behavior) |
| `stagnation_flag` | 🟢 Computed from real wind speed | **LIVE** | `wind < 2.0 m/s` — fires 0% of days (too windy for stagnation) |
| `sirocco_flag` | 🟢 Computed from real wind dir + speed | **LIVE** | `120°-220°` AND `> 8 m/s` |
| `rain_flag` | 🟢 Computed from real precipitation | **LIVE** | `precip > 2mm` |
| `sea_breeze` | 🔴 Always `False` | **HARDCODED** | `"sea_breeze": False` — never computed |

